title: 'Good purchase'
body: Build quality good enough for eighteen liters capacity bucket and feels sturdy while using it. Price is also decent as per the price point and how long it will last depend on its usage that's obvious. Not sure of being food grade so I use it for water storage purpose of daily misllenous needs.

title: 'Backet cracks'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. Scratches'

title: 'Bucket quality is poor'
body: 'The bucket is having colour variations in all the parts. The bucket is not sturdy. I have placed the return but no one is come to pick the bucket. Pathetic service offered by Amazon.'
